fields.name: CurrentFirmwareVersion
fields.description: Version string of the firmware currently installed on this Cache.

fields.name: FirmwareUpdateDeadline
fields.description: Time at which the pending firmware update will automatically be installed on the Cache.

fields.name: FirmwareUpdateStatus
fields.description: True if there is a firmware update ready to install on this Cache. The firmware will automatically be installed after firmwareUpdateDeadline if not triggered earlier via the upgrade operation.

fields.name: LastFirmwareUpdate
fields.description: Time of the last successful firmware update.

fields.name: PendingFirmwareVersion
fields.description: When firmwareUpdateAvailable is true, this field holds the version string for the update.
